<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Reservation Confirmed</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
        <h2 style="color: #0056b3; margin: 0;">Reservation Confirmed! 🎉</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
        <p>Hi <strong>{{ user.username }}</strong>,</p>
        
        <p>Great news! Your reservation for the event has been confirmed by the administration.</p>
        
        <div style="background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #495057;">Event Details:</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>📅 Event:</strong> {{ event.title }}</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>⏰ Date:</strong> {{ event.date|date('F j, Y, g:i a') }}</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>📍 Location:</strong> {{ event.location }}</li>
                <li><strong>🎟️ Seats Reserved:</strong> {{ reservation.seats }}</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Events Management Team</strong></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
